snippet.title: Arcade Game: Flash Boy (1981 Data East)
snippet.description:
A superhero action flying game.

Also known as "The Deco Kid" outside Japan.

Gameplay starts at 3:39

Note: Used invincibility cheat after down to last life. The game is endless so I quit afterwards.
